""" vim keybindings

" With a map leader it's possible to do extra key combinations
" like <leader>w saves the current file
"let mapleader = "\<Space>"
let mapleader = ";"


"" Fast saving && quit
nmap <leader>w :w!<cr>
" :W sudo saves the file
command W w !sudo tee % > /dev/null
nmap <leader>W :W<cr>

" 定义快捷键关闭当前 buffer
nmap <Leader>q :Bclose<CR>
" 不做任何保存,直接退出 vim
nmap <Leader>Q :qa!<CR>


"" Moving
" 行首、行尾与文件开头、文件结尾
nmap H 0
nmap L $

" PageUp and PageDown
nmap K <C-B>
nmap J <C-F>


" 定义快捷键在结对符之间跳转,助记 pair
