"" toggle number line
function! HideNumber()
  if(&relativenumber == &number)
    set relativenumber! number!
  elseif(&number)
    set number!
  else
    set relativenumber!
  endif
  set number?
endfunc

nnoremap <Leader>nl :call HideNumber()<CR>


"" Copy && paste
" Toggle paste mode on and off
set pastetoggle=<Leader>P


" 设置快捷键将选中文本块复制至系统剪贴板
